snippet.description:
As our America 250 POTA rove continues, we stop at US-1625, Monmouth Battlefield State Park in New Jersey.  The band conditions were much better than the past couple of days and the activation was going well.  Then, I get a surprise call on the radio from AD2CD asking to come by the park.  I was THRILLED.  Tobi is one of the most prolific Hunters in the POTA world.  I've hoped for a chance to meet her and she's on her way to the park.  Once she arrives, we do a brief dual activation.  It was so so much fun.  Thank you Tobi.
#parksontheair 
#pota 
#potaantenna 
#hamradio 
#hamradio 
#hamradioantenna 
#portableradio 

Equipment used:
 @YaesuUSAOfficial  FT-891
 @corallee8451  JPC-12
 @ABRindCoax  Coax
 @ecoworthy_official  20ah Battery
 @GigaPartsHuntsville  
 @DXEngineering  
@TobiAD2CD 

Thanks for watching.  Please LIKE and consider subscribing to the channel.
73
Paul
KJ5GKK

