snippet.description:
America 250 POTA rove continues at US-0062, Saratoga National Historical Park.  We were late getting into the park and oh, by the way, it's FIELD DAY 2026!  What the heck was I thinking!  It was nothing short of a train wreck.  Every 1/2 kc was being used for Field Day.  And, don't get me wrong, that's a great thing.  If I was back home in Louisiana, I'd be working Field Day too.  But today I just want to get US-0062 activated. The crazy thing is I was able to work 3 great DX stations in order to help me get my contacts. Come along to see how this works out.
#parksontheair 
#pota 
#hamradio 
#hamoperator 
#america250 
#portableradio

Equipment used:
@YaesuUSAOfficial FT-891
@ABRindCoax Coax
@ChameleonAntennaOfficial SS-17
@ecoworthy_official 20ah battery
@LDGElectronics-2 Z-100 Plus antenna tuner
@RigExpert_Ukraine Stick 230

Thanks for watching and please subscribe if you enjoyed the video.
Paul
KJ5GKK

